Package: mirDIP
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the mirDIP Web API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jaime", family = "User", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com")
)
Description: A lightweight R client to query the mirDIP web service
    for unidirectional and bidirectional searches of gene symbols and
    microRNAs. Provides helpers to parse responses into convenient
    R structures.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jaimefalcon/mirDIP-R
BugReports: https://github.com/jaimefalcon/mirDIP-R/issues
